description:
Indulge in luxury with the Esita Crystal Cupcake Clutch—a dazzling statement piece that blends elegance with playfulness. Designed to resemble a deliciously detailed cupcake, this handbag is encrusted with shimmering, high-quality crystals in a mesmerizing mix of colors, creating a rich, eye-catching sparkle.

The structured, compact design features a gold-tone clasp closure and a detachable chain strap, allowing for versatile styling as a handheld clutch or a chic shoulder bag.
